        "accordion_item_BQRfcT": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_title": "Details",
            "accordion_content": "<p>Your morning coffee may do more than wake you up. Franky is the complete morning formula with real coffee flavor, real nutrition, and functional ingredients that may help carry you through the entire morning from the first sip.</p><p>Each serving delivers <strong>10g of whey protein concentrate</strong>, which may help reduce hunger, manage cravings, and support lean muscle during weight loss. Combined with <strong>3 billion CFU probiotics</strong> and <strong>1,500mg of psyllium husk fiber</strong>, it may help support digestion, reduce bloating, and keep mid-morning cravings at bay.</p><p>Weight: </p><p>Then there's the focus stack. <strong>300mg of lion's mane mushroom</strong> extract and <strong>200mg of L-theanine</strong> pair with <strong>50mg of natural caffeine</strong> for calm, steady energy that may help you stay sharp, without the jitters or crash.</p><p><strong>Zero sugar</strong>. <strong>No artificial fillers. Gluten-free, soy-free, and keto-friendly</strong>. Add two scoops to cold water or milk over ice, shake, and you're done in under 60 seconds. And it actually tastes incredible: rich, smooth vanilla hazelnut that you may find yourself looking forward to every single morning. <strong>Made in the USA.</strong></p><p>20 Servings · Net Weight 11.1 oz (314g) </p><p>Price per Serving: </p><p>1 Bag: $1.99/serving<br/>2 Bags: $1.43/serving · Save 28%<br/>3 Bags: $1.35/serving · Save 32%</p><p></p><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_BMU6dj": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_title": "Benefits & Ingredients",
            "accordion_content": "<p>Franky combines real coffee with <strong>10g of protein and functional ingredients</strong> designed to support steady energy, focus, and satiety. Instead of the typical caffeine spike and crash, the formula provides smoother energy through balanced caffeine and L-theanine.<br/>The blend includes <strong>protein for sustained fuel</strong>, <strong>natural caffeine for focus</strong>, and <strong>prebiotic fiber to support digestion and gut balance</strong>. Together, these ingredients help turn your morning coffee into a more complete and functional routine.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_fpnbqj": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_title": "Nutritional Information",
            "accordion_content": "<p>Each serving of Franky contains <strong>10g of protein</strong>, balanced caffeine comparable to a cup of coffee, and a low-sugar formula designed to support steady energy.<br/>The formula is<strong> keto</strong>-<strong>friendly</strong> and <strong>gluten</strong>-<strong>free</strong>, with no fillers or unnecessary additives.  </p><p>Our Protein Coffee is a light and energizing choice, with just <strong>67 calories per serving</strong>. If you prefer a stronger boost and add two scoops, the total comes to <strong>134 calories. </strong>Still a low-calorie option that fits perfectly into an active lifestyle.</p><p></p>",
            "accordion_image": "shopify://shop_images/Franky_Nutritional_Info.png"
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_hdeJXf": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_title": "How to Enjoy",
            "accordion_content": "<p>Add one scoop to Cold Water, Hot Water, or your Milk of Joy — almond milk over a mountain of ice is our personal favorite. Shake or stir, done in 60 seconds flat. No blender, no barista, no drama.</p><p>Best served ice cold. Make it your morning ritual and you'll actually look forward to your alarm going off. Almost.</p><p><br/>Many people use Franky as part of their <strong>morning routine or as a light breakfast alternative</strong>, providing energy, focus, and satiety without the typical coffee crash.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_UgPTiM": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_title": "Shipping & Returns",
            "accordion_content": "<p><strong>Standard Shipping</strong><br/>3–5 business days · Free on orders over $50 · $4.95 on orders under $50</p><p><strong>Express Shipping</strong><br/>1–2 business days · $9.95</p><p>Orders ship from our Georgia warehouse within 1 business day.</p><p><strong>30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</strong><br/>Not happy? Zero risk — just reach out and we'll make it right.</p>"
          }
        },
