    "maison_faq_QLFLjc": {
      "type": "maison-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_item_x7BFRN": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What does it taste like?",
            "answer": "<p>Living well shouldn't mean giving up what you love — it should mean upgrading it.</p><p>Franky Protein Coffee tastes like your favorite coffee, just better. Incredibly creamy, rich, and smooth — with a subtle vanilla-hazelnut note and a natural sweetness that makes every sip genuinely enjoyable. Mix two scoops with your go-to milk and you've got something worth waking up for.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_acLwN7": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is NOT in Franky Protein Coffee?",
            "answer": "<p>Let's be frank: what we leave out matters just as much as what we put in.</p><p><strong>No Sugar. No Fillers. No Compromises.</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Sugar:</strong> 0g per serving. Period.</li><li><strong>Sucrose:</strong> No table sugar hiding under a different name.</li><li><strong>Stevia:</strong> We use Monk Fruit Extract and Fermented Reb M instead, for a cleaner, smoother sweetness with zero bitter aftertaste.</li><li><strong>Dextrose & Maltodextrin:</strong> No cheap filler carbs that spike your blood sugar.</li><li><strong>Corn Syrup or High-Fructose Corn Syrup:</strong> None. Not even a trace.</li><li><strong>Seed Oils:</strong> No canola, soybean, sunflower, or other inflammatory oils.</li><li><strong>Artificial Sweeteners:</strong> No aspartame, sucralose, or acesulfame-K.</li><li><strong>Artificial Colors or Flavors:</strong> Nothing synthetic. Ever.</li><li><strong>Fillers or Proprietary Blends:</strong> Every ingredient is listed with its exact dose. No mystery formulas, no hidden shortcuts.</li><li><strong>Gluten:</strong> 100% gluten-free.</li><li><strong>Soy:</strong> Completely soy-free.</li><li><strong>GMOs:</strong> Non-GMO verified.</li><li><strong>Pesticides:</strong> Made with organically grown ingredients.</li><li><strong>Heavy Metals:</strong> Every batch is third-party lab tested for purity and safety.</li></ul><p>You deserve to know exactly what you're putting in your body: and exactly what you're not. That's why our label is fully transparent and our formula stays clean, always.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_Gc3cd8": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How much protein per serving?",
            "answer": "<p>Each scoop contains <strong>10g of high-quality protein</strong>. For best results, we recommend two scoops per serving, giving you 20g of protein that may fuel your morning, support muscle recovery, keep you satisfied, and work toward your weight loss goals.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_G9iCMV": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How many calories?",
            "answer": "<p>Our Protein Coffee is a light and energizing choice, with just <strong>67 calories per serving</strong>. If you prefer a stronger boost and add two scoops, the total comes to <strong>134 calories. </strong>Still a low-calorie option that fits perfectly into an active lifestyle. </p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_Ermbtx": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will it keep me full until lunch?",
            "answer": "<p>That's exactly what it's designed for. The combination of 20g of whey protein (two scoops) and 1,500mg of psyllium husk fiber may help reduce hunger and cravings, keeping you satisfied and away from unnecessary snacking until lunch.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_BUczLQ": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will I crash or get jitters?",
            "answer": "<p>No. Franky contains 50mg of balanced caffeine combined with 200mg of L-theanine, which may help smooth out the energy boost — and may give you calm, focused energy with no spike, no jitters, and no mid-morning crash. With two scoops, you're getting 100mg, roughly the equivalent of a regular cup of coffee.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_gH3kcf": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is it good for gut health?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Every serving contains 3 billion CFU of clinically studied probiotics and 1,500mg of psyllium husk fiber, which may support healthy digestion, help reduce bloating, and contribute to a balanced gut microbiome.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_AkrewH": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I prepare it?",
            "answer": "<p>Add one or two scoops to 8oz of cold water or your favorite milk, almond or regular milk over ice works best. Shake or stir well and enjoy. No coffee machine, no blender, no prep, ready in under 60 seconds.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_yrAef3": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Does it contain dairy or allergens?",
            "answer": "<p>Franky contains whey protein concentrate, which is derived from milk, and is not suitable for those with a dairy allergy or intolerance. It is <strong>100</strong>% <strong>gluten</strong>-<strong>free</strong> and <strong>non</strong>-<strong>GMO</strong>. Please review the full ingredient list before purchasing if you have any specific dietary concerns.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
